metadata.name: Free Bird
metadata.description:
To celebrate 10K twitter followers, Free Bird is a gift to those who have supported me in my NFT journey.

I photographed this Great Horned Owl in the Sonoran Desert of southern Arizona. This is a digital art piece with a hand painted background and digitally painted effects.
